PhD on Tantric iconography. The caretaker sat under a tree outside, reading a newspaper.\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Inside the circle, the only sound was wind through the open roof. The yoginis looked outward from their niches, toward the rice fields, toward the distant highway, toward whatever they have been looking at for eleven hundred years.\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"I sat on the floor in the centre of the circle for a long time, not meditating exactly, just being still in a place that asked for stillness.\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The woman from Kolkata came and sat nearby. We didn't speak. We didn't need to.\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"hr\\\",null,{}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"em\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Location: Hirapur village, ~9 km from Bhubaneswar. ASI protected. Open daily sunrise to sunset.\\\"}]}]]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"16:[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"meta\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"charSet\\\":\\\"utf-8\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"meta\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"name\\\":\\\"viewport\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\\\"}]]\\n12:null\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1f:I[622,[],\\\"IconMark\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"14:{\\\"metadata\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"title\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The Sixty-Four Yoginis of Hirapur | SuDhama\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"meta\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"name\\\":\\\"description\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Hidden in a field nine kilometres from Bhubaneswar, a circular roofless temple holds sixty-four yoginis in sandstone — among the rarest religious sites in India.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"meta\\\",\\\"2\\\",{\\\"property\\\":\\\"og:title\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"The Sixty-Four Yoginis of Hirapur\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"meta\\\",\\\"3\\\",{\\\"property\\\":\\\"og:description\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"H