tant highway, toward whatever they have been looking at for eleven hundred years.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"I sat on the floor in the centre of the circle for a long time, not meditating exactly, just being still in a place that asked for stillness.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The woman from Kolkata came and sat nearby. We didn't speak. We didn't need to.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"hr\",null,{}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"em\",null,{\"children\":\"Location: Hirapur village, ~9 km from Bhubaneswar. ASI protected. Open daily sunrise to sunset.\"}]}]]\n16:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n12:null\n1f:I[622,[],\"IconMark\"]\n14:{\"metadata\":[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"The Sixty-Four Yoginis of Hirapur | SuDhama\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"Hidden in a field nine kilometres from Bhubaneswar, a circular roofless temple holds sixty-four yoginis in sandstone — among the rarest religious sites in India.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"The Sixty-Four Yoginis of Hirapur\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"3\",{\"property\":\"og:description\",\"content\":\"Hidden in a field nine kilometres from Bhubaneswar, a circular roofless temple holds sixty-four yoginis in sandstone — among the rarest religious sites in India.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"4\",{\"property\":\"og:image\",\"content\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620766182578-02435699aa59?q=80&w=1600\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"5\",{\"name\":\"twitter:card\",\"content\":\"summary_large_image\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"6\",{\"name\":\"twitter:title\",\"content\":\"The Sixty-Four Yoginis of Hirapur\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"7\",{\"name\":\"twitter:description\",\"content\":\"Hidden in a field nine kilometres from Bhubaneswar, a circular roofless temple holds sixty-four yoginis in sandstone — among the rares